# Authorization and Role Gating

If role-based access is introduced, enforce explicit permissions and least privilege.

## Requirements
- Define roles and permissions in a single shared module.
- Gate high-risk actions (bulk export, data purge, debug bundle export) behind explicit user confirmation.
- Keep authorization checks in the orchestration layer, not just in UI controls.

## Notes
- Today the extension is single-user; treat this as future-proofing, not active enforcement.
